From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: Hinduonnet.com (edited)
<http://www.hinduonnet.com/thehindu/thscrip/print.pl?file=2003081410780300.htm&date=2003/08/14/&prd=th&>

Two more cholera cases
----------------------
Two more cases of cholera were reported from the Tiruvallam area in the
city. So far there have been 13 cases of confirmed cholera during the
outbreak of diarrheal disorders.
[byline: Kerala Thiruvanathapuram]
